Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.80,0:01:26.90,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,へえ　蟲師
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.74,0:01:32.24,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あ　何か具合の悪いところや奇妙なことでもあれば
