Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.03,0:02:07.09,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何の　いろいろ変わった話が聞けて面白かったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.54,0:02:11.53,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,俺ら　平凡に暮らしてきたからな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.11,0:02:15.41,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何ごともないのが一番いいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.95,0:02:19.58,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,まあ　そうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.95,0:02:22.39,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,それじゃ　達者で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.55,0:02:24.29,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ああ　あんたもな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.98,0:03:44.28,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,すっかり遅くなっちまったな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.15,0:03:49.80,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,早く帰らねぇと　あいつが心配する
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.39,0:03:59.38,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,花の…匂い
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.86,0:04:03.01,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,まただ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.96,0:04:08.35,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,また何か大事なことを忘れてるような…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.55,0:04:17.64,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,こんな洞があったかな
