Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.13,0:13:33.93,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,今も思うんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.36,0:13:41.09,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,こんな雨の晩に　前にもあんたを家に泊めた事がある…と
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.87,0:13:45.93,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,俺はこの辺りに来るのは初めてだがな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.77,0:13:51.98,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そうか　いやまあ　だからどうということもないんだが
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.14,0:13:56.01,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ただ　どうにも気が落ち着かなくてな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.02,0:13:59.65,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,こんなことは稀にあることなのかと
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.60,0:14:06.19,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,既視感か
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.10,0:14:12.46,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,もしや　夜　花の匂いを嗅ぐと不安になる…とか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.39,0:14:18.09,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ああ　そうだ 何かを忘れてる気がして
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.41,0:14:26.56,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そうか　あんたは「廻陋」に囚われちまったのかもしれんな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.35,0:14:33.08,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,花のような匂いを出し　虫や獣を誘い込む
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.36,0:14:35.25,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,漆黒の筒状の蟲だ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.10,0:14:42.89,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そして　誘い込んだ獲物の時間を円環状に歪めると言われている
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.70,0:14:51.05,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,だとすれば　そいつは同じ時間を繰り返し生かされることになる
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.81,0:14:54.33,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,繰り返し…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.21,0:14:58.94,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,誰にも確かめる術はない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.21,0:15:02.73,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,が　もし　そうだとしたら
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.86,0:15:07.52,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あんたはもう同じ人生を何度も生きているんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.89,0:15:12.73,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そして　この先の何処かでまた
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.43,0:15:15.39,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,同じように廻陋に出くわす
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.10,0:15:20.64,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,気付かずにまたその中を潜ってしまえば
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.50,0:15:24.94,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,また時間は繰り返し　同じ人生を味わう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.81,0:15:28.89,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,既視感を持つ者の記録はあるが
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.88,0:15:32.41,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,全てを調べることなど到底できない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.38,0:15:37.78,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そいつの人生の全てを知るなんてことは
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.49,0:15:46.71,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,同じことを…俺は繰り返し…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.03,0:15:51.21,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何一つ言い切ることはできんが
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.90,0:15:56.11,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,一応　花の匂いのする暗がりには用心したほうがいい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.27,0:16:00.83,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,廻陋に囚われた者が
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.41,0:16:04.00,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,思うように過去を変えたという話は聞かない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.15,0:16:09.17,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,それに　既視感を持ったということは
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.89,0:16:12.98,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,今までのように昔に戻ることはできないかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.79,0:16:20.21,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何度も潜るうちに　廻陋と同化してしまうかもしれん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.03,0:16:26.77,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,決して　もう一度潜ろうなどとは考えるなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.04,0:16:35.72,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,変えたい過去もあるが
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.54,0:16:40.54,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,それより俺はこの先が見たい
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.31,0:16:46.61,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,娘の成長や孫の姿や　
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.55,0:16:50.80,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,まだ見たことのない毎日がな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.78,0:17:08.77,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,おーい　郁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:12.65,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,山菜取りに行ってくるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.58,0:17:16.22,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そう　気をつけてね
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.96,0:17:24.38,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,すっかり遅くなっちまったな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.00,0:17:28.70,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,早く帰らねぇと
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.62,0:17:45.81,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ああ　そうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.42,0:17:52.17,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,俺は何度もこの穴を潜った後　あの頃に戻って
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.04,0:18:22.12,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,カオル　遅かったじゃない　何かあったの？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.05,0:18:27.57,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ああ　このお前は初めて見る
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.56,0:18:35.36,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ずっと幸せな悪夢を見ていたようだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.29,0:18:39.59,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何よそれ　どうしたの　一体
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.64,0:18:47.37,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,これからはずっと新しい毎日がやって来るんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.47,0:19:15.39,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あれ　郁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.04,0:19:19.93,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,おい　どこだ　
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.95,0:19:21.80,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,郁…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.55,0:19:30.51,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,辛抱しろ　すぐ医者に連れてってやるからな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.02,0:19:35.67,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,体は冷たくなってく
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.83,0:19:38.95,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,どうすれば
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.90,0:19:41.74,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,このままじゃ　里に着く前に…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.32,0:20:04.98,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,決して　もう一度潜ろうなどとは考えるなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.96,0:20:14.57,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,なあ　郁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.83,0:20:19.43,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,この中から花の匂いがする
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.21,0:20:23.37,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,里への近道かもしれん
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.64,0:20:29.47,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,大丈夫だよ　お前は助かるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.98,0:20:39.07,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そしてまた　遠い未来に　俺と一緒に暮らすんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.48,0:21:03.36,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ほら
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.11,0:21:06.33,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.57,0:21:31.80,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あれ　今　何か思い出しそうな気がした
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.70,0:21:35.99,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,郁　どうかしたのか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.42,0:21:40.23,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ううん　何でもない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.29,0:21:44.08,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,一体何だったかしら
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.13,0:21:52.84,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何か懐かしいような　恐ろしいような
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.27,0:21:59.55,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,どちらさんだい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.27,0:22:03.63,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,旅の者だが　この雨で難儀している
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.38,0:22:06.32,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,一晩軒を借りられんだろうか
